                                        <a href="@Url.Action(MVC.PvP.OwnerAction("restrain",  (int)ViewBag.ItemId))" class="check itemCheck inanimateAction">Forcibly restrain your @Model.PlayerForm.Form.FriendlyName (Block action)</a>
                                    </li>
                                }
